title: Diluvio
actors: Daniel Olbrychski, Malgorzata Braunek, Tadeusz Lomnicki, Kazimierz Wichniarz, Wladyslaw Hancza, Leszek Teleszynski, Ryszard Filipski, Wieslawa Mazurkiewicz, Franciszek Pieczka, Leslaw Janicki, Waclaw Janicki, Bruno O'Ya, Wlodzimierz Bednarski, Bogusz Bilewski, Andrzej Kozak
description: During the 1655 war between Protestant Sweden and Catholic Polish-Lithuanian Commonwealth some Polish-Lithuanian nobles side with Swedish king Charles X Gustav while others side with the Polish king Jan Kazimierz.
